Iraqi blogger [_Salam Pax_](http://twitter.com/Salam/status/1315364624) warns
all shoe throwers in this Tweet: “..alert to all shoe throwers.. hide your
shoes! 3yrs jail for attacking Bush with shoe, and missing!” Muntadar Al
Zaidi, who threw his shoes at President George W Bush during a Press
conference in Iraq last year, was
[sentenced](http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7938947.stm) to three years
in jail.

